      "type": "topic",
      "content": "<p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><p><br></p><h3><strong>Topics → World → (Cosmology, History, Regions, Races, Factions)</strong></h3><h3><strong>Characters → (Sherwins, Faelivrin, Dragonborn, Ancients)</strong></h3><h3><strong>Timeline → (Ages, Wars, Key Events)</strong></h3><h3><strong>Maps → (Gontha, Elise, Eden, Scaron, Tausa, Legend Island)</strong></h3><p>Everything is nested cleanly, infinitely expandable, and mirrors Obsidian’s vault logic.+</p><p><br></p>",
