        ]
      },
      "content": "<p><br></p><div class=\"ql-table-embed\"><table style=\"border-collapse: collapse; table-layout: fixed; width: 1106px; margin-left: auto; display: table; float: none; margin-right: auto;\" data-table-align=\"center\" data-clear-border=\"1\"><tbody><tr><td contenteditable=\"true\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"textbox\" style=\"border: 1px solid rgb(228, 198, 47); background: transparent; padding: 4px; width: 100%; vertical-align: top;\" class=\"\" data-clear-border=\"1\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\">&nbsp;</span><h2 style=\"font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><br class=\"Apple-interchange-newline\"><img src=\"assets/encyclopedia_2.png\" data-resizable=\"true\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; max-width: 100%; height: auto; user-select: none; cursor: default !important;\" class=\"\"></span></h2><h2 style=\"font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></span></h2><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><span class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">🌌 </span><strong class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 20px;\">Core Identity of the Setting</strong></span></p><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><span class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">The world is a </span><strong class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">dual‑realm cosmology</strong><span class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 14px;\">:</span></span></p><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></span></p><ul style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style-type: none; padding-left: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><strong class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Earth</strong><span class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">, where humanity originates, fractured by war and later reshaped by crystal‑based technology.</span></span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style-type: none; padding-left: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><strong class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Exodus (Ellavian/Gontha)</strong><span class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">, the </span><strong class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">fae‑rooted dreamworld</strong><span class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> where imagination becomes reality and where the actions of humans and Ancients ripple across galaxies.</span></span></li></ul><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><span class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">The two realms are linked through </span><strong class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">the Books of Time</strong><span class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">, </span><strong class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Balance Crystals</strong><span class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">, and </span><strong class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Gatebridges</strong><span class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">, forming a metaphysical system where cosmic law, magic, and prophecy intertwine. As the text states, </span><em class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">“The vast worlds of the Extal galaxy are governed by the Sacred Books of Time… What transpires on Exodus… reflect onto Earth in dreams and imagination.”</em></span></p><h2 style=\"font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></span></h2><h2 style=\"font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\">📚 The Cosmic Framework</span></h2><h3 style=\"font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; font-size: 1.17em; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\">The Four Books of Time</span></h3><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><span class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">These books are the </span><strong class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">cosmic operating system</strong><span class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> of the Extal galaxy.</span></span></p><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\">Each book governs a different aspect of reality:</span></p><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></span></p><ul style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style-type: none; padding-left: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><strong class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Book of Time</strong><span class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> — records and regulates cosmic events; written by Father Time under Elyon’s command. </span><em class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">“The hand of God is written on all four Books of Time and they obey His commands.”</em></span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style-type: none; padding-left: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><strong class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">The Curse</strong><span class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> — chronicles humanity’s fall and the consequences of their corruption.</span></span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style-type: none; padding-left: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><strong class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Gate Bridges</strong><span class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> — contains the secrets of interworld travel and rewriting reality.</span></span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style-type: none; padding-left: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><strong class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Prophecy of Dragons</strong><span class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> — reveals the fate of Dragonborn, humans, and the ultimate fall of Extal.</span></span></li></ul><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\">These books are forbidden to mortals and guarded by Ancients.</span></p><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></span></p><h2 style=\"font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\">🔮 Magic, Power, and the Balance Crystals</span></h2><h3 style=\"font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; font-size: 1.17em; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\">The Balance Crystals</span></h3><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><span class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">The Crystals are the </span><strong class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">heartbeats of the fae worlds</strong><span class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">, stabilizing magic, nature, and even time.</span></span></p><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><span class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Your text notes: </span><em class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">“Without the Crystals’ energy, all life on Exodus… would cease to exist.”</em></span></p><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><span class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Two major Balance Crystals—</span><strong class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Adrylin</strong><span class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> and </span><strong class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Tausa</strong><span class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">—anchor the worl</span></span></p><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></span></p><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></span></p><ul style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style-type: none; padding-left: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><strong class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Tausa</strong><span class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> was shattered, unleashing storms and earthquakes and allowing dark forces to steal its swords. </span><em class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">“The results were worldwide earthquakes and wild storms… The swords… were taken by the Neverworld soldiers.”</em></span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style-type: none; padding-left: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><strong class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Adrylin</strong><span class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> barely survived destruction thanks to Ardil, a chosen hero guided by angels and Ancients.</span></span></li></ul><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\">The shattering of Tausa is one of the most important turning points in the world’s metaphysical stability.</span></p><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><br></span></p><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></span></p><h2 style=\"font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\">🐉 Races, Ancients, and Dragonborn</span></h2><h3 style=\"font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; font-size: 1.17em; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\">The Ancients</span></h3><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><span class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Elves, dwarves, dragons, giants, phantoms, and other mythic beings originate from the dream‑essence of Exodus. They are the </span><strong class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">firstborn of imagination</strong><span class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">, predating humanity.</span></span></p><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><br></span></p><h3 style=\"font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; font-size: 1.17em; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\">Dragonborn</span></h3><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\">A hybrid race created through dark experimentation by James Faelivrin, later redeemed and elevated by Elyon.</span></p><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><span class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">They become </span><strong class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">guardians, emissaries, and peacekeepers</strong><span class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"> between humans and Ancients.</span></span></p><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\">Your text describes them as:</span></p><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Lora;\">“Redeemed with truth and Elyon’s own grace, they became the protectors of both ancients, native creatures and humans.”</em></p><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\">Their history includes:</span></p><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><br></span></p><ul style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style-type: none; padding-left: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\">A Holy War against Faelivrin</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style-type: none; padding-left: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\">The founding of Dragonborn’s Realm in the Midlands</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style-type: none; padding-left: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\">A civil war that nearly destroyed them</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style-type: none; padding-left: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\">Their eventual disappearance, leaving the world vulnerable</span></li></ul><h2 style=\"font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></span></h2><h2 style=\"font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; font-size: 1.5em; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\">⚔️ The White Council and Human Corruption</span></h2><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\">The White Council is the dominant magical and religious authority among humans.</span></p><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><span class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">They worship the </span><strong class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Nine Gods</strong><span class=\"ql-font-lora\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">, enforce magical law, and rewrite history to maintain power.</span></span></p><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\">Your text notes:</span></p><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><em style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Lora;\">“The White Council plays dirty… to go against them means dire consequences.”</em></p><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\">They:</span></p><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\"><br></span></p><ul style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 1.5em; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style-type: none; padding-left: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\">Control magic through White Priests, War Mages, and Pentarch Wizards</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style-type: none; padding-left: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\">Persecute Wild Magic and Seekers</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style-type: none; padding-left: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\">Erase records of Dragonborn and ancient history</span></li><li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style-type: none; padding-left: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\">Manipulate kingdoms through religious fear</span></li></ul><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family: Lora;\">They are a major antagonist force in the setting.</span></p><p style=\"cursor: text; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; counter-reset: list-1 0 list-2 0 list-3 0 list-4 0 list-5 0 list-6 0 list-7 0 list-8 0 list-9 0; color: rgb(242, 242, 242); font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; caret-color: rgb(242, 242, 242); white-space: pre-wrap; 